{"tid":534031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《文革之禍》『莫須有』- 文革流氓紅衛兵把岳武穆及其子屍骨被「挫骨揚灰」","createTime":"2018-01-19T11:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T12:16:29.000Z","uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba119ee609becf1a865bdc26d4ad7b299df91b44","tid":534031,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"岳飛墓，處於杭州西湖棲霞嶺南麓，建於南宋嘉定十四年（1221年），碑刻有「宋岳鄂王墓」，左側為其子宋繼忠侯岳雲墓。中共文化大革命期間，流氓紅衛兵破壞岳廟，墓闕被推倒，連岳飛及岳雲的墳也被夷為平地，岳武穆及其子屍骨被「挫骨揚灰」，讓人不忍卒睹。<br />\n<br />\n（資料來源：秋海棠民國史地，此圖片取自1923年出版的《 Picturesque China - Architecture and Landscape - A Journey through Twelve Provinces 》，此書乃德國建築師及歷史學者Ernst Boerschmann於光緒卅二年至宣統元年（1906-1909）間對我國古建築進行考察和研究之圖文集。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/194245_1c07a0770bea38e73a71edae2c76b798.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F194245_1c07a0770bea38e73a71edae2c76b798.png&h=cba81040&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce4ccad3b8b5fbc7b5095611f2c431260bdfd740","tid":534031,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521e0144b795e6fa8623d9183a895480437b612e","tid":534031,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"元清朝都未及支那共朝萬分一"},{"pid":"5dd9b783ae2228543567bcb96cac9c0b841ba531","tid":534031,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}